CS537 Homework Assignment 2: Drawing 2D Polygons with Color
Author: Bingyao Huang
Date: 01/20/2016
Language: C++

This code uses OpenGL to draw multiple colored geometries in two windows.

Contents:
	source files: main.cpp, part2.cpp, InitShader.cpp
	makefile: Makefile
	library folder: include
	

Usage:	
	make: the default target compiles all the code
	make run: executes the program(s)
	make clean: deletes all the object files and executable files.
	
	

	

